COMMENT @----------------------------------------------------------------------

MESSAGE:	NTakerDocumentNewNote -- MSG_NTAKER_DOC_NEW_NOTE
						for NTakerDocumentClass

DESCRIPTION:	Create a new note

PASS:
	*ds:si - instance data
	es - segment of NTakerDocumentClass

	ax - The message

RETURN:

