						for NTakerDocumentClass

DESCRIPTION:	Change notes (user selected a different note)

PASS:
	*ds:si - instance data
	es - segment of NTakerDocumentClass

	ax - The message

	cx - note number

RETURN:
	nothing
DESTROYED:
	bx, si, di, ds, es (message handler)

